<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">If this option is active, new passwords must meet the criteria set for password security.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Minimum length</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter the minimum number of characters for new passwords.<br>
