<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter the number of previously used passwords that users cannot use again. If the user tries to enter a previously used password, the user is asked to enter a different password. If you do not want to use this function, enter 0 or leave blank.<br>
<strong><em>Note:</em></strong> The number of passwords to be saved must be 20 or less.</p></td>
</tr>
