<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Define a colour in the editing window by selecting a colour, entering a hexadecimal colour code or the RGB value. The colour makes it easier to identify the user account in other menus, for example the <a href="/en/welcome/general-functions/tasks-and-calendars#600">Calendar</a>.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Time zone</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Select the user’s time zone.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>Image URL</strong></p></td>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">Enter an image URL here, for example to insert a thumbnail image used for blog entries.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock"><strong>UI language</strong></p></td>
