<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="120">6.3. Managing menu and REST API rights</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>In the <strong>Authorisations</strong> tab, you specify which rights for the REST API are granted to a user account of the <strong>Back end</strong> access. No REST API rights are activated by default. User accounts of the <strong>Admin</strong> access have all rights.</p>
</div>
