<p>Click on the <strong>Rights</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Managing menu and REST API rights</strong>.<br>
→ The <strong>Rights</strong> menu item opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Assign the rights for the respective area by ticking the check boxes. Activate entire areas or expand areas to activate individual rights that the user account should have access to.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> (<span class="icon green"><i class="fa fa-save  "></i></span>) the settings.</p>
</li>
